Insider Activity


Individual




Stephen G. Waldis



Mr. Stephen G. Waldis is Executive Chairman & Chief Executive Officer at Synchronoss Technologies, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at ClickFox, Inc., Factor Systems, Inc., New Jersey Technology Council and Seton Hall University. Mr. Waldis was previously employed as Chief Operating Officer by The Vertek Corp., Vice President-Sales & Marketing by Logical Design Solutions, Inc., and a Principal by AT&T, Inc. He also served on the board at Intralinks Holdings, Inc. He received his undergraduate degree from Seton Hall University.



